content: How can I improve th e fill rate for these products?

SELECT DISTINCT ITEM as Item, RES as Resource , ROUND(prodrate,2) AS Production_Rate ,ROUND(max_prodrate,2) as Max_Production_Rate,ROUND((max_prodrate-prodrate),2) as Increase_In_TPH, ROUND(yield,2) AS Yield, ROUND(max_yield,2) as Max_Yield, ROUND((max_yield-yield),2) as Increase_In_Yield from ABP_DATA;
